replies.body:
Tahm is another champion along the line of those that can severely screw up yourself and your own team.

Along with the likes of {{champion:12}} , {{champion:432}} , {{champion:34}} , {{champion:53}} , {{champion:40}}  and also {{summoner:12}} 

The wall with him is not mechanical skill but how good your decision making is. You need to think beyond "can I?" to "should I?" to use him effectively.
